Redis Info Plugin
======================
Created by [Matt Todd](http://twitter.com/mtodd)
Extended by [Ches Martin](http://whiskeyandgrits.net) and [Josh Nichols](http://technicalpickles.com)

Overview
------------

Reports Redis metrics extracted from Redis' `info` command:

 * Uptime
 * Memory Used
 * Connections per Second
 * Commands per Second
 * Connected Clients
 * Connected Slaves
 * Changes Since Last Save

Also generates alerts when redis goes down and comes back up.

Dependencies
------------

Requires the ruby Redis client library ('redis' gem).
